## Flat / Time-Series Entity Type Detection

### Context
Added a heuristic mechanism to detect entity types that behave like flat datasets
or time series (e.g. `MeterReading`, `RawEvent`). The detection runs in a single
extra pass over the triples already in memory inside `GraphMetrics.compute()` —
no additional database query needed.

### Changes
1. `src/back/core/graph_analysis/models.py` — added `EntityTypeProfile` dataclass
